The paper discusses the usage of blockchain technology for business process management, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also explores the suitability of the Bitcoin blockchain for this purpose, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the implementation of a software prototype, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the evaluation of the prototype, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.DL) and databases (cs.DB).
